title: TV | First Dates: Celebrity Special for SU2C
text: It's a special celebrity First Dates tonight as part of the Stand Up To Cancer TV special as maitre d' Fred and his team welcome hopeful single people from across the country who are unaware that some of the dinner dates will be famous faces. The celebs are set to include Alexandra Burke and Anthea Turner with the regular Joes' including Swiss-born neuroscience student Sophie and personal trainer Craig.
